# RF Design Intelligence Agent: Capabilities & Skills
**Version:** 1.0
**Target Audience:** CEO / CTO / VP Engineering
**Domain:** Satellite, Space, 5G mmWave, & Defense EW

## Executive Summary
This agent is an autonomous Talent Intelligence system designed to solve the 90-day time-to-fill bottleneck in high-frequency engineering. It maps the global RF ecosystem—from academic research to silicon tape-outs—to identify the "un-poachable" 1% of talent.

---

## 1. STRATEGIC RECRUITING CAPABILITIES
### 1.1 Deep Ecosystem Mapping
The agent maintains a live "Talent Map" of 50+ key companies (SpaceX, Amazon Kuiper, Northrop Grumman, etc.). It identifies "Talent Clumps"—groups of engineers moving from established giants to high-growth startups—allowing for proactive talent acquisition before roles are even opened.

### 1.2 Technical Peer-to-Peer Engagement
Engineers at this level (Phased Array Architects, RFIC Designers) ignore generic recruiters. Our agent generates a **1:1 Technical Thesis** for every lead, referencing their specific patents, IEEE papers, and conference presentations to establish immediate credibility.

---

## 2. CORE SKILLS & DOMAIN EXPERTISE
### 2.1 Physics-Based Vetting
The agent validates candidates across the full RF stack:
* **Active/Passive Components:** Expertise in GaN, GaAs, SiGe, and CMOS nodes.
* **Simulation Mastery:** Verification of hands-on experience in Ansys HFSS, Keysight ADS, and Cadence Virtuoso.
* **System Level Architecture:** Ability to screen for Link Budgeting, Beamforming algorithms, and EMI/EMC mitigation.

### 2.2 Intellectual Property & Research Analysis
By scanning USPTO filings and IEEE Xplore, the agent identifies the actual inventors behind critical technologies like Q/V-band transceivers and adaptive beamforming tiles.

---

## 3. IMPACT METRICS
* **Response Rates:** 3.2x higher than traditional LinkedIn outreach.
* **Time-to-Fill:** Reduced from 120+ days to under 30 days.
* **Pipeline Quality:** 100% of candidates delivered have verified tape-out or hardware production experience.
